            <font size="2">
             <span style="font-family: Georgia,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">
              Emma Victoria Payne is a wedding dress designer known
  for exquisite, vintage inspired bridal gowns, Emma Victoria Payne 
 wedding dresses are perfect for the modern bride with an elegant, yet 
 timeless quality.
              <br/>
              <br/>
             </span>
            </font>
           </font>
           At Ana Cristache London &amp; Emma Victoria Payne Bridalwear, we make bespoke and made to measure bridal wear to the highest quality standards. We design and create exclusive custom made and made to measure wedding dresses and every year we have a new collection of beautiful wedding dresses.
           <br/>
          </span>
          <br/>
          From our Beauchamp Place, Knightsbridge wedding dress shop we are able to create any wedding dress design required, not just designs that are part of our wedding dress collection. Brides who choose to have a bespoke wedding dress always have a say in the development of their unique custom made design. We take pride in working as a team with each bride to create their dream wedding dress.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          Our bridal gowns are priced from £2,000 - £4,000 for a made to measure collection or
         </font>
        </font>
        <font size="3" style="font-family: Georgia,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">
         <font size="2">
          <font size="3" style="font-family: Georgia,Times New Roman,Times,serif;">
           <font size="2">
            £2,500 - £6,000 for a
           </font>
          </font>
          bespoke wedding dress. We also have the La Sposa bridal collection, part of the Pronovias Group Wedding Dresses which is priced from £1,000-£2,000. Our Elie Saab collection gowns are priced from £5,500-£10,000.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          When making a bespoke wedding dress (a new custom made design that is not part of our collection), we are able to give a quote once we know all the details involved. We hold consultations only by appointment in our Knightsbridge boutique, at no financial obligation. We are able to schedule appointments also in the evening and on Saturdays.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          If you are looking for a custom made wedding dress dress, please call or e-mail our Park Walk, Chelsea, London shop if you wish to make an appointment to view our collection of wedding dresses or to discuss our bespoke bridal wear and made to measure services.
          <br/>
